snippet.title: Town of Salem Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the game at:
https://www.blankmediagames.com/TownOfSalem

Like our Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/TownOfSalemGame

Follow us on Twitter:
https://www.twitter.com/TownOfSalemGame

Inspired by the party games Werewolf and Mafia, Town of Salem is a free-to-play game of murder, mystery and deception.
